comment:
* Columns in the StreamItemPhotos table.
     *
     * @see ContactsContract.StreamItemPhotos
     * @deprecated - Do not use. This will not be supported in the future. In the future,
     * cursors returned from related queries will be empty.
     *
     * @removed

variables.name: STREAM_ITEM_ID
variables.comment:
* A reference to the {@link StreamItems#_ID} this photo is associated with. *

Type: NUMBER

* * @deprecated - Do not use. This will not be supported in the future. In the future, * cursors returned from related queries will be empty.

variables.name: SORT_INDEX
variables.comment:
* An integer to use for sort order for photos in the stream item. If not * specified, the {@link StreamItemPhotos#_ID} will be used for sorting. *

Type: NUMBER

* * @deprecated - Do not use. This will not be supported in the future. In the future, * cursors returned from related queries will be empty.

variables.name: PHOTO_FILE_ID
variables.comment:
* Photo file ID for the photo. * See {@link ContactsContract.DisplayPhoto}. *

Type: NUMBER

* * @deprecated - Do not use. This will not be supported in the future. In the future, * cursors returned from related queries will be empty.

variables.name: PHOTO_URI
variables.comment:
* URI for retrieving the photo content, automatically populated. Callers * may retrieve the photo content by opening this URI as an asset file. *

Type: TEXT

* * @deprecated - Do not use. This will not be supported in the future. In the future, * cursors returned from related queries will be empty.
